caption: Table 1: Experimental results on synthetic and real-world datasets for GNN expressivity (Acc.%)
description: This table presents the classification accuracy results of different Graph Neural Network (GNN) models on several benchmark datasets.  The datasets include both synthetic datasets designed to test the expressive power of GNNs (CSL, EXP, SR25) and real-world datasets for protein function prediction (ENZYMES, PROTEINS).  The table shows the number of parameters for each model and their respective accuracy (Acc.%) on each dataset.  The results highlight the performance of the proposed Deep Homomorphism Network (DHN) model in comparison to existing GNNs.

caption: Table 1: Experimental results on synthetic and real-world datasets for GNN expressivity (Acc.%)
